Q1.  Recurrence for Merge Sort
------------------------------
What is the recurrence relation for merge sort ?

Options
This problem has only one correct answer:
1. T(n) = 2T(n/2)
2. T(n) = 2T(n/2) + k
3. T(n) = 2T(n/2) + O(n) 
4. T(n) = 2T(n/2) + O(log n)

Solution(3)

